snippet: The Golden State Warriors took advantage of a short-handed Dallas Mavericks squad to record a 52nd consecutive home-court victory, riding another record-setting 3-point-shooting performance to a hard-earned 128-120 win....
lead_paragraph: The Golden State Warriors took advantage of a short-handed Dallas Mavericks squad to record a 52nd consecutive home-court victory, riding another record-setting 3-point-shooting performance to a hard-earned 128-120 win.

headline.main: Warriors Chalk Up 52nd Straight Home Win
headline.print_headline: Warriors Chalk Up 52nd Straight Home Win
